description:
Daaaaaaaang Dalton is cute!
He is just one of the nicest, level-headed guys too. AND CUTE!
Dalton said he would be up for an oral video, but thought that would be his limit. He does pretty dang good, and I'm hoping that he will come back for more. But as of this writing, he hit his limit, so this might be it for him.
This is a Serviced video you have to watch the whole thing. By whole thing, I mean even the stuff beyond the end credits. You will see just how good he is (or I am!)
Highlight for me was flipping him over and eating his ass, something he never had done, which left him a bit speechless afterwords. I could see the machinery and cogs churning in his mind with all kinds of ideas to try with a girlfriend.
Anyway, enjoy this 2-4-2sday!
title: Bryan & Dalton - Serviced
